org.purl.co.interfaces
Interface COItem<E>

All Known Subinterfaces:
COListItem<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
StandardCOItem, StandardCOListItem
public interface COItem<E>

This interface represents a CO item, that is a particular object used in the CO ontology for allowing repetition of elements within a bag or list.

Author:
Paolo Ciccarese, Silvio Peroni
